"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An enclosed, uncovered area within the precincts of large buildings such as temples, palaces and houses. The wilderness tabernacle also incorporated a courtyard.</p>\n<h2>The courtyard of the tabernacle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:9-Exod27:19\">EXO 27:9–27:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:9-Exod38:20\">EXO 38:9–38:20</a></p>\n<h2>The courtyard of the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:64\">1KI 8:64</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:7\">2CH 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:9\">2CH 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:5\">2CH 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:21\">2CH 24:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:2\">JER 26:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:10\">JER 36:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:14\">EZK 40:14</a></p>\n<h2>Courtyards of palaces</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:11\">EST 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:2\">JER 32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:15\">JER 39:15</a></p>\n<h2>Courtyards of private houses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:16\">NEH 8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:18\">2SA 17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:69\">MAT 26:69</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:66\">MRK 14:66</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:55\">LUK 22:55</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:15\">JHN 18:15</a></p>",
